headline: Is job growth really negative right now? Morgan Stanley answers
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley told investors in a note that recent comments from Federal Reserve officials about the possibility of negative U.S. job growth may be overstating the degree of labour-market weakness, even as hiring cools and unemployment edges higher.
